        <h1 itemprop="headline">Response to Calais crisis will not resolve situation</h1>

        
                <h3>PREDICTABLY another day of chaos at Calais has yielded another Cobra committee meeting and the politicians have again failed to take the decisive action necessary.</h3>
        
